{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gzweb/issues/30/comments/7777943.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gzweb/issues/30#comment-7777943"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gzweb/issues/30.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 30, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gzweb.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gzweb"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{3e2fc3f2-dc25-453b-9792-943c743d9b40}ts=1609263"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "gzweb", "full_name": "osrf/gzweb", "uuid": "{3e2fc3f2-dc25-453b-9792-943c743d9b40}"}, "title": "Make the grid a different color from the ground plane"}, "content": {"raw": "The gazebo grid color is set in [gazebo::rendering::Scene::SetGrid](https://bitbucket.org/osrf/gazebo/src/6f357235d464f26f5ffc61f90e17e67f788703f5/gazebo/rendering/Scene.cc?at=default#cl-2694). For some reason there's two grids defined there with different colors.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>The gazebo grid color is set in <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"https://bitbucket.org/osrf/gazebo/src/6f357235d464f26f5ffc61f90e17e67f788703f5/gazebo/rendering/Scene.cc?at=default#cl-2694\" rel=\"nofollow\">gazebo::rendering::Scene::SetGrid</a>. For some reason there's two grids defined there with different colors.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2014-01-17T02:08:53.248014+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comme